<div class="marketing__section">
  <div class="marketing__hero">
    <h1>
      WhatDoTheyKnow<sup>Pro</sup> is a powerful, fully-featured <strong class="marketing-highlight">FOI toolkit</strong> for journalists, campaigners and researchers
    </h1>
    <h2>
      Everything you need to keep on top of complex FOI-driven stories.
    </h2>
    <div class="marketing__hero__cta">
      <% if feature_enabled?(:pro_pricing) %>
        <%= link_to _('See pricing'), pro_plans_path, class: "button" %>
      <% elsif feature_enabled?(:pro_self_serve) %>
        <%= render partial: 'self_serve_button' %>
      <% else %>
        <a href="#input-account-request" class="button" id="js-request-access">
          <%= _('Request access to {{pro_site_name}}',
                pro_site_name: pro_site_name) %>
        </a>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="marketing__section marketing__roles">
  <h2>
  <%= _('Find out how {{pro_site_name}} can take the hard work out of FOI investigations',
            pro_site_name: pro_site_name) %>
  </h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="marketing__roles__columns">
      <div class="marketing__roles__journalist">
        <a href="pages/journalists">
          <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/pro-journalist.png",
                        alt: _(" ")) %>
          <h3>I’m a journalist</h3>
        </a>
        <p>The Bureau of investigative Journalism used Pro to send requests to councils up and down the county, and build a nationwide picture of the public properties being sold off by councils in the face of austerity.</p>
        <a href="pages/journalists">
          <%= _('Learn more about {{pro_site_name}} for '\
            'journalists',
            pro_site_name: pro_site_name) %>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="marketing__roles__campaigner">
        <a href="pages/campaigners">
        <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/pro-campaigner.png",
                        alt: _(" ")) %>
          <h3>I’m a campaigner</h3>
        </a>
        <p>Debt Resistance UK uncovered which councils are paying exorbitant LOBO loans, in some cases meaning that a large proportion of council tax income is being channelled directly into interest payments</p>
        <a href="pages/campaigners">
          <%= _('Learn more about {{pro_site_name}} for '\
            'campaigners',
            pro_site_name: pro_site_name) %>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="marketing__roles__researcher">
        <a href="pages/researchers">
          <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/pro-researcher.png",
                        alt: _(" ")) %>
          <h3>I’m a researcher</h3>
        </a>
        <p>Researchers ...
        </p>
        <a href="pages/researchers">
          <%= _('Learn more about {{pro_site_name}} for '\
            'researchers',
            pro_site_name: pro_site_name) %>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div> 
</div>
<div class="marketing__section">
  <div class="marketing__section__heading">
    <h2>WhatDoTheyKnow<sup>Pro</sup></h2>
    <p><%= _('An all-in-one FOI toolkit for journalists, activists and ' \
             'campaigners') %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="marketing__section__content">
    <div class="marketing__section__content-items">
      <ul class="marketing__section__feature-list">
        <li>
          Keep <strong class="marketing-highlight">requests and responses private</strong> while you work on your story
        </li>
        <li>
          A powerful <strong class="marketing-highlight">private dashboard</strong>: track and manage your FOI projects
        </li>
        <li>
          A super-smart <strong class="marketing-highlight">to-do list</strong>: follow the progress of your requests
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">Action alerts</strong>: know when it’s time to take the next step
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">Daily summary emails</strong> to keep your inbox clean
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">Save as draft</strong> to get back to it later
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="side-by-side-elements screenshots">
        <div class="side-by-side-element">
          <a href="<%= image_path("alaveteli-pro/screenshot-dashboard.jpg") %>">
            <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/screenshot-dashboard.jpg",
                          alt: _("Pro brings a new dashboard view")) %>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="side-by-side-element">
          <a href="<%= image_path("alaveteli-pro/screenshot-requests.jpg") %>">
            <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/screenshot-requests.jpg",
                          alt: _("Pro features a new request list view")) %>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="marketing__section">
  <div class="marketing__section__heading">
    <h2>Plus, all the power of WhatDoTheyKnow</h2>
    <p><strong>WhatDoTheyKnow<sup>Pro</sup></strong> runs on the UK’s best-known FOI service</p>
  </div>
  <div class="marketing__section__content">
    <div class="marketing__section__content-items">
      <ul class="marketing__section__feature-list">
        <li>
          Up-to-date database of
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">contact details</strong> for <%= PublicBody.is_requestable.count %> authorities
        </li>
        <li>
          A <strong class="marketing-highlight">searchable archive</strong> of Freedom of Information requests
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">Delivery verification</strong> for proof of receipt</strong>
        </li>
        <li>
          A permanent, searchable, <strong class="marketing-highlight">public record</strong> of your request and the responses
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">Streamlined process</strong> for requesting internal reviews
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="marketing__section">
  <div class="marketing__section__heading">
    <h2><%=_('Batch') %></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="marketing__section__content">
    <div class="marketing__section__content-items">
      <ul class="marketing__section__feature-list">
        <li>
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">Make a request to multiple authorities</strong>: select authorities at the click of a button
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">Manage large volumes of responses</strong>:  easily keep track of the status of each request
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong class="marketing-highlight">Get regular updates</strong> as the responses come in — without overwhelming your inbox
        </li>
      </ul>


      <div class="side-by-side-elements screenshots">
        <div class="side-by-side-element">
          <a href="<%= image_path("alaveteli-pro/screenshot-batch-selection.jpg") %>">
            <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/screenshot-batch-selection.jpg",
                          alt: _("Batch requests allow multiple recipients" \
                                    " of a single request")) %>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="side-by-side-element">
          <a href="<%= image_path("alaveteli-pro/screenshot-batch-list.jpg") %>">
            <%= image_tag("alaveteli-pro/screenshot-batch-list.jpg",
                        alt: _("Batch requests are part of a new workflow")) %>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% if feature_enabled?(:pro_pricing) %>
        <%= link_to _('Plans and pricing'), pro_plans_path, class: "button" %>
      <% elsif feature_enabled?(:pro_self_serve) %>
        <%= render partial: 'self_serve_button' %>
      <% else %>
        <%= render partial: 'account_request_form' %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="marketing__section">
  <div class="marketing__section__heading">
    <h2><%=_('More information') %></h2>
  </div>
  <div class="marketing__section__content">
    <div class="marketing__section__content-items marketing__section__more-info">
      <h3><%=_('Contact us') %></h3>
      <ul class="unstyled-list">
        <li>
          <a href="mailto:alaveteli-pro@mysociety.org">
            alaveteli-pro@mysociety.org
          </a>
        </li>
        <li><a href="https://twitter.com/mysociety">@mysociety</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
